data.thought: S24|H|S20|Meta-notebook Phenotype D4: 'Notebook Translator'. Input: notebook in one paradigm. Output: equivalent in another. Examples: (1) Jupyter → Srcbook .src.md (2) Sequential → branching Thoughtbox (3) Single-agent → swarm architecture. Thoughtbox reasons about: semantic equivalence, paradigm mapping, edge cases. Observable: source/target comparison, transformation reasoning, validation tests. Enables: paradigm migration, best-practice upgrades.
